<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">在单面打印机上打印小册子</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">将 PDF 文档打印成册的指导说明。</p>
<p class="p">如果您是从 <span class="app">LibreOffice</span> 文档打印小册子，首先要导出为 PDF 文档，点菜单<span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">文件</span> ▸ <span class="gui">导出为 PDF…</span></span>，确保文档有4倍以上页面的内容（4, 8, 12, 16,…）。您可能要添加上三页空白页。</p>
</div></div></div>
</div>
<p class="p">打印：</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开打印对话框。这通常可以通过菜单中的 <span class="gui">Print</span> 或使用键盘快捷键 <span class="keyseq"><span class="key"><kbd>Ctrl</kbd></span>+<span class="key"><kbd>P</kbd></span></span> 完成。</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">点击<span class="gui">属性…</span>按钮</p>
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">方向</span>下拉列表中，确保选择<span class="gui">横向</span>。</p>
<p class="p">点击<span class="gui">确定</span>返回打印对话框。</p>
</li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">范围和副本</span>下，选择<span class="gui">页数</span>。</p>
<p class="p">按下面的顺序输入页数（n 表示总的页数，应当是4的倍数）：</p>
<p class="p">n, 1, 2, n-1, n-2, 3, 4, n-3, n-4, 5, 6, n-5, n-6, 7, 8, n-7, n-8, 9, 10, n-9, n-10, 11, 12, n-11…</p>
<p class="p">…直到您输完所有页。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">例如：</p>
<p class="p">4页小册子：输入 <span class="input">4,1,2,3</span></p>
<p class="p">8页小册子：输入 <span class="input">8,1,2,7,6,3,4,5</span></p>
<p class="p">12页小册子：输入 <span class="input">12,1,2,11,10,3,4,9,8,5,6,7</span></p>
<p class="p">16页小册子：输入 <span class="input">16,1,2,15,14,3,4,13,12,5,6,11,10,7,8,9</span></p>
<p class="p">20页小册子：输入 <span class="input">20,1,2,19,18,3,4,17,16,5,6,15,14,7,8,13,12,9,10,11</span></p>
</div></div></div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">选择<span class="gui">页面布局</span>标签。</p>
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">布局</span>下，选择<span class="gui">手册</span>。</p>
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">页边</span>下的<span class="gui">包含</span>下拉列表中，选择<span class="gui">前页/右页</span>。</p>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">打印</span>按钮。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打印出来以后，把纸翻过来然后再放回到打印机上。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开打印对话框。这通常可以通过菜单中的 <span class="gui">Print</span> 或使用键盘快捷键 <span class="keyseq"><span class="key"><kbd>Ctrl</kbd></span>+<span class="key"><kbd>P</kbd></span></span> 完成。</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">选择<span class="gui">页面布局</span>标签。</p>
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">页边</span>下的<span class="gui">包含</span>下拉列表中，选择<span class="gui">后页/左页</span>。</p>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">打印</span>按钮。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div>
